name: WormArt - Heart of the Fire
description:
Original photography fed to the ravenous Algorithm Worms which secrete a delightful pigment trail as they happily writhe around the canvas.

The small Western Australian town of Dardanup has an annual festival day called the Bull and Barrel. The culmination of the event is the burning of a huge piece of wooden artwork using the bull theme. This piece was seeded with a photograph staring into the heart of this bonfire.

3000x3000.
